LOW_POWER_SUPPORT

static final java.lang.String LOW_POWER_SUPPORT

CONTROL_BACK_INTERCEPT

static final java.lang.String CONTROL_BACK_INTERCEPT
If true presses on the Control.KeyCodes.KEYCODE_BACK will be sent to the Control extension in Control.Intents.CONTROL_KEY_EVENT_INTENT intents. This allows the Control extension to implements its own handling. If false a press on the Control.KeyCodes.KEYCODE_BACK will stop the control.

TYPE: BOOLEAN

PRESENCE: OPTIONAL (Default false)

Since:
2.0
